high_descs: Go straight ahead until reaching the hallway on the right, then turn to the hallway and go down it, entering the third door on the left into the bathtub.
Pick up the butterknife from the bathtub.
Exit this bathroom the way you came in, then go to the door in front and slightly to the left, approaching the bread at the far end of the room.
Slice the bread on the table.
Look down at the desk.
Place the butterknife down on the desk.
Look back to the sliced bread on the desk.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Exit this room the way you came in, go left through the hallway all the way until you reach the kitchen area on your right, then turn into it and approach the microwave at the corner of the counters.
Use the microwave on the sliced bread and remove the bread.
Go to the fridge to your left.
Put the bread inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a microwaved slice of Bread into a Fridge.

high_descs: Go forward and then turn right to go down the hall to the bathtub on the left.
Pick up the butterknife from the bathtub.
Turn around, exit the bathroom and go left to the first room on the right and go to the brown bread.
Cut the bread on the table.
Look up from the desk.
Place the butterknife on the desk.
Look down toward the bread on the desk.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn around, exit the room and go left down the hall and turn right into the kitchen to the microwave.
Put the bread slice into the microwave, turn the microwave on and then take out the bread.
Turn left and go to the side of the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the bread slice inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed Bread in the Fridge.
